<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV68">
<l>muttiṟattu vāṇiyatti raṇṭiloṉṟu nīcarkaḷ</l>
<l>mattarāyma yaṅkukiṉṟa tiṭṭatili ṟantupōn</l>
<l>tettiṟattu muyvatōru pāyamillai yuykuṟil</l>
<l>tottiṟutta taṇṭuḻāynaṉ mālaivāḻtti vāḻmiṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lowly people who join the two [guṇas] out of the threefold fruits,</l>
<l>Become confused, being bewildered. There is no means of any kind</l>
<l rend="indent">for [their] salvation</l>
<l>As [they] place [their karman] there, die, and go [into another womb].</l>
<l>If [you] desire salvation, live [by] praising the good Māl with cool tulsi</l>
<l rend="indent">tied in a bunch.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
